token_fundings()`, `apply_sol_fundings()` |\n| `cache` | `CacheMeta`, `resolve_cache_state()`, `derive_cache_key_single()`, `derive_cache_key_bundle()`, `write_meta_json()`, `read_meta_json()` |\n| `idl_fetcher` | `IdlFetcher`, `get_idl_address()` |\n| `account_file` | `parse_account_json()` |\n| `native_ids` | `is_native_or_sysvar()`, `NATIVE_PROGRAM_IDS` |\n| `progress` | `ProgressReporter` (trait) |\n\n## 4. 详细改动清单\n\n### 4.1 新建文件\n\n#### `crates/sonar-sim/Cargo.toml`\n\n```toml\n[package]\nname = \"sonar-sim\"\nversion = \"0.1.0\"\nedition = \"2021\"\ndescription = \"Solana transaction simulation engine powered by LiteSVM\"\n\n[dependencies]\nanyhow = \"1.0\"\nbase64 = \"0.22\"\nbs58 = \"0.5\"\nbincode = \"1.3\"\nlog = \"0.4\"\nserde = { version = \"1.0\", features = [\"derive\"] }\nserde_json = { version = \"1.0\", features = [\"preserve_order\"] }\nlitesvm = \"0.8.1\"\nsha2 = \"0.10.9\"\nflate2 = \"1.0\"\nhex = \"0.4\"\n\n# Solana SDK\nsolana-account = \"3.0\"\nsolana-clock = \"3.0\"\nsolana-hash = \"3.0\"\nsolana-pubkey = \"3.0\"\nsolana-transaction = \"3.0\"\nsolana-transaction-status-client-types = \"3.0\"\nsolana-rpc-client-types = \"3.0\"\nsolana-client = \"3.0\"\nsolana-message = \"3.0\"\nsolana-address-lookup-table-interface = \"3.0\"\nsolana-commitment-config = \"3.0\"\nsolana-slot-hashes = \"3.0\"\nsolana-loader-v3-interface = \"6.1.0\"\nsolana-rent = \"3.0\"\nsolana-sdk-ids = \"3.0\"\nsolana-sysvar-id = \"3.0\"\nsolana-signature = \"3.0\"\nsolana-system-interface = { version = \"3.0\", features = [\"bincode\"] }\n\n# SPL Token\nspl-token = \"9.0.0\"\nspl-token-2022 = \"10.0.0\"\nspl-pod = \"0.7.1\"\n\n[dev-dependencies]\nsolana-keypair = \"3.0\"\nsolana-signer = \"3.0\"\n```\n\n#### `crates/sonar-sim/src/progress.rs`\n\n```rust\nuse std::borrow::Cow;\n\n/// 进度回调 trait，用于解耦 UI 层。\n///\n/// 库使用者实现此 trait 以接收长时间操作的进度通知。\n/// CLI 可以用 indicatif 实现，GUI 可以用自己的进度条，\n/// 测试中可以传入 no-op 实现。\npub trait ProgressReporter: Send + Sync {\n    /// 更新当前进度消息。\n    fn set_message(\u0026self, msg: Cow\u003c'static, str\u003e);\n\n    /// 标记操作完成。默认空实现。\n    fn finish(\u0026self) {}\n}\n```\n\n### 4.2 移动文件（src/core/ → crates/sonar-sim/src/）\n\n每个文件需要做的通用修改：\n\n1. **内部引用**：`crate::core::xxx` → `crate::xxx`\n2. **native_ids**：`crate::utils::native_ids::` → `crate::native_ids::`\n3. **Progress 类型**：`crate::utils::progress::Progress` → `dyn crate::progress::ProgressReporter`\n4. **可见性**：`pub(crate)` → `pub`（需要对外暴露的类型和函数）\n\n以下为每个文件的具体改动：\n\n---\n\n#### `executor.rs`\n\n**引用变更**：\n```rust\n// Before\nuse crate::core::{\n    account_loader::{ResolvedAccounts, ResolvedLookup},\n    funding::{PreparedTokenFunding, apply_sol_fundings},\n    types::{AccountDataPatch, Funding, Replacement},\n};\n\n// After\nuse crate::{\n    account_loader::{ResolvedAccounts, ResolvedLookup},\n    funding::{PreparedTokenFunding, apply_sol_fundings},\n    types::{AccountDataPatch, Funding, Replacement},\n};\n```\n\n**可见性变更**：\n```rust\n// Before\npub(crate) fn dump_accounts_to_dir(...) -\u003e Result\u003c()\u003e { ... }\n\n// After\npub fn dump_accounts_to_dir(...) -\u003e Result\u003c()\u003e { ... }\n```\n\n**native_ids 引用**：\n```rust\n// Before\ncrate::utils::native_ids::is_native_or_sysvar(pubkey)\n\n// After\ncrate::native_ids::is_native_or_sysvar(pubkey)\n```\n\n---\n\n#### `account_loader.rs`\n\n**Progress 解耦**（最关键的改动）：\n\n```rust\n// Before\nuse crate::utils::progress::Progress;\n\npub struct AccountLoader {\n    ...\n    progress: Option\u003cProgress\u003e,\n    ...\n}\n\nimpl AccountLoader {\n    pub fn new(\n        rpc_url: String,\n        local_dir: Option\u003cPathBuf\u003e,\n        cache_write_dir: Option\u003cPathBuf\u003e,\n        offline: bool,\n        progress: Option\u003cProgress\u003e,\n    ) -\u003e Result\u003cSelf\u003e { ... }\n}\n\n// After\nuse std::sync::Arc;\nuse crate::progress::ProgressReporter;\n\npub struct AccountLoader {\n    ...\n    progress: Option\u003cArc\u003cdyn ProgressReporter\u003e\u003e,\n    ...\n}\n\nimpl AccountLoader {\n    pub fn new(\n        rpc_url: String,\n        local_dir: Option\u003cPathBuf\u003e,\n        cache_write_dir: Option\u003cPathBuf\u003e,\n        offline: bool,\n        progress: Option\u003cArc\u003cdyn ProgressReporter\u003e\u003e,\n    ) -\u003e Result\u003cSelf\u003e { ... }\n}\n```\n\n**移除 `idl_fetcher()` 方法**，改为暴露 provider：\n\n```rust\n// Before\npub fn idl_fetcher(\u0026self, progress: Option\u003cProgress\u003e) -\u003e IdlFetcher {\n    IdlFetcher::with_provider(Arc::clone(\u0026self.provider), progress.or_else(|| self.progress.clone()))\n}\n\n// After\n/// 获取底层 RPC provider，允许调用方构造 IdlFetcher 等衍生对象。\npub fn provider(\u0026self) -\u003e Arc\u003cdyn RpcAccountProvider\u003e {\n    Arc::clone(\u0026self.provider)\n}\n```\n\n**其他引用变更**：\n```rust\n// Before\nuse crate::{\n    core::{idl_fetcher::IdlFetcher, rpc_provider::*, transaction::*, types::Replacement},\n    utils::progress::Progress,\n};\n\n// After\nuse crate::{\n    rpc_provider::*,\n    transaction::*,\n    types::Replacement,\n    progress::ProgressReporter,\n};\n```\n\n**`#[cfg(test)]` 的 `with_provider` 改为 pub**（库使用者也需要注入 mock）：\n\n```rust\n// Before\n#[cfg(test)]\npub fn with_provider(...) -\u003e Self { ... }\n\n// After\npub fn with_provider(\n    provider: Arc\u003cdyn RpcAccountProvider\u003e,\n    local_dir: Option\u003cPathBuf\u003e,\n    offline: bool,\n    progress: Option\u003cArc\u003cdyn ProgressReporter\u003e\u003e,\n) -\u003e Self { ... }\n```\n\n---\n\n#### `rpc_provider.rs`\n\n**`FakeAccountProvider` 从 `#[cfg(test)]` 提升为公开类型**（放入 `testing` feature 或直接公开）：\n\n```rust\n// Before\n#[cfg(test)]\npub struct FakeAccountProvider { ... }\n\n// After — 方案 A：直接公开（简单）\npub struct FakeAccountProvider { ... }\n\n// After — 方案 B：feature gate（更严谨）\n#[cfg(any(test, feature = \"testing\"))]\npub struct FakeAccountProvider { ... }\n```\n\n推荐方案 A（简单直接），因为 `FakeAccountProvider` 只是一个轻量 in-memory mock。\n\n---\n\n#### `funding/mod.rs`\n\n**Progress 解耦**：\n```rust\n// Before\nuse crate::utils::progress::Progress;\n\npub fn prepare_token_fundings(\n    loader: \u0026AccountLoader,\n    resolved: \u0026mut ResolvedAccounts,\n    requests: \u0026[TokenFunding],\n    progress: Option\u003c\u0026Progress\u003e,\n) -\u003e Result\u003cVec\u003cPreparedTokenFunding\u003e\u003e { ... }\n\n// After\nuse crate::progress::ProgressReporter;\n\npub fn prepare_token_fundings(\n    loader: \u0026AccountLoader,\n    resolved: \u0026mut ResolvedAccounts,\n    requests: \u0026[TokenFunding],\n    progress: Option\u003c\u0026dyn ProgressReporter\u003e,\n) -\u003e Result\u003cVec\u003cPreparedTokenFunding\u003e\u003e { ... }\n```\n\n**引用变更**：\n```rust\n// Before\nuse crate::{\n    core::{account_loader::*, types::*},\n    utils::progress::Progress,\n};\n\n// After\nuse crate::{\n    account_loader::*,\n    types::*,\n    progress::ProgressReporter,\n};\n```\n\n---\n\n#### `idl_fetcher.rs`\n\n**Progress 解耦**：\n```rust\n// Before\nuse crate::utils::progress::Progress;\n\npub struct IdlFetcher {\n    provider: Arc\u003cdyn RpcAccountProvider\u003e,\n    progress: Option\u003cProgress\u003e,\n}\n\n// After\nuse crate::progress::ProgressReporter;\n\npub struct IdlFetcher {\n    provider: Arc\u003cdyn RpcAccountProvider\u003e,\n    progress: Option\u003cArc\u003cdyn ProgressReporter\u003e\u003e,\n}\n```\n\n**引用变更**：\n```rust\n// Before\nuse crate::core::rpc_provider::*;\nuse crate::utils::progress::Progress;\n\n// After\nuse crate::rpc_provider::*;\nuse crate::progress::ProgressReporter;\n```\n\n---\n\n#### `transaction.rs`\n\n**移除无用的 Progress 参数**：\n```rust\n// Before\npub fn fetch_transaction_from_rpc(\n    rpc_url: \u0026str,\n    signature: \u0026str,\n    _progress: Option\u003c\u0026Progress\u003e,\n) -\u003e Result\u003cString\u003e { ... }\n\n// After\npub fn fetch_transaction_from_rpc(\n    rpc_url: \u0026str,\n    signature: \u0026str,\n) -\u003e Result\u003cString\u003e { ... }\n```\n\n同步更新 `parse_transaction_input` 中的调用：\n```rust\n// Before\nlet fetched = fetch_transaction_from_rpc(rpc_url, input, progress)?;\n\n// After\nlet fetched = fetch_transaction_from_rpc(rpc_url, input)?;\n```\n\n**引用变更**：\n```rust\n// Before\nuse crate::utils::progress::Progress;\n\n// After\n// (removed — no longer needed)\n```\n\n---\n\n#### `cache.rs`\n\n**可见性变更**（所有 `pub(crate)` → `pub`）：\n```rust\n// Before\npub(crate) struct CacheMeta { ... }\npub(crate) fn resolve_cache_dir(...) -\u003e PathBuf { ... }\npub(crate) fn derive_cache_key_single(...) -\u003e String { ... }\npub(crate) fn derive_cache_key_bundle(...) -\u003e String { ... }\npub(crate) fn resolve_cache_state(...) -\u003e (Option\u003cPathBuf\u003e, bool) { ... }\npub(crate) fn write_meta_json(...) -\u003e Result\u003c()\u003e { ... }\npub(crate) fn read_meta_json(...) -\u003e Result\u003cCacheMeta\u003e { ... }\n\n// After\npub struct CacheMeta { ... }\npub fn resolve_cache_dir(...) -\u003e PathBuf { ... }\npub fn derive_cache_key_single(...) -\u003e String { ... }\npub fn derive_cache_key_bundle(...) -\u003e String { ... }\npub fn resolve_cache_state(...) -\u003e (Option\u003cPathBuf\u003e, bool) { ... }\npub fn write_meta_json(...) -\u003e Result\u003c()\u003e { ... }\npub fn read_meta_json(...) -\u003e Result\u003cCacheMeta\u003e { ... }\n```\n\n**引用变更**：\n```rust\n// Before\nuse crate::core::transaction;\n\n// After\nuse crate::transaction;\n```\n\n---\n\n#### `native_ids.rs`\n\n**可见性变更**：\n```rust\n// Before\npub(crate) static NATIVE_PROGRAM_IDS: LazyLock\u003cHashSet\u003cPubkey\u003e\u003e = ...;\npub(crate) fn is_native_or_sysvar(pubkey: \u0026Pubkey) -\u003e bool { ... }\n\n// After\npub static NATIVE_PROGRAM_IDS: LazyLock\u003cHashSet\u003cPubkey\u003e\u003e = ...;\npub fn is_native_or_sysvar(pubkey: \u0026Pubkey) -\u003e bool { ... }\n```\n\n---\n\n#### `balance_changes.rs`, `account_file.rs`, `types.rs`\n\n这三个文件没有对 `crate::core::*` 或 `crate::utils::*` 的引用，直接迁移即可，无需修改。\n\n---\n\n#### `funding/sol.rs`, `funding/token_legacy.rs`, `funding/token2022.rs`\n\n**引用变更**：\n```rust\n// Before\nuse crate::core::types::Funding;\nuse crate::core::account_loader::ResolvedAccounts;\n\n// After\nuse crate::types::Funding;\nuse crate::account_loader::ResolvedAccounts;\n```\n\n### 4.3 修改 sonar 二进制 crate\n\n#### 根 `Cargo.toml`\n\n```toml\n# 新增 workspace 配置\n[workspace]\nmembers = [\".\", \"crates/sonar-sim\"]\n\n[dependencies]\n# 新增\nsonar-sim = { path = \"crates/sonar-sim\" }\n\n# 以下依赖可从根 Cargo.toml 中移除（已迁入 sonar-sim）：\n# - litesvm\n# - sha2\n# - flate2\n# - solana-loader-v3-interface\n# - solana-slot-hashes\n# - solana-address-lookup-table-interface\n# - solana-rent\n# - solana-sysvar-id\n# - solana-clock\n# - solana-epoch-schedule\n# - solana-nonce\n# - spl-pod\n\n# 以下依赖保留（CLI/parsers/output 仍需使用）：\n# - clap, clap_complete, env_logger, colored, indicatif\n# - toml, terminal_size, unicode-width, chrono, num-bigint\n# - spl-token-metadata-interface, spl-token-group-interface\n# - solana-account, solana-pubkey, solana-transaction, solana-message\n#   (output/parsers 模块仍直接使用这些类型)\n# - serde, serde_json, base64, bs58, bincode, hex, log\n#   (可能被多个模块共用)\n```\n\n**注意**：需要仔细检查哪些 solana-* 依赖在 `parsers/`、`output/`、`handlers/` 中被直接使用。保守做法是先保留所有依赖，编译后逐步移除未使用的。\n\n#### `src/core/mod.rs` — 替换为 re-export 层\n\n```rust\n// 将 src/core/ 下的所有 .rs 文件删除，仅保留 mod.rs\n// 通过 re-export 保持 crate::core::xxx 路径兼容\n\npub use sonar_sim::account_file;\npub use sonar_sim::account_loader;\npub use sonar_sim::balance_changes;\npub use sonar_sim::cache;\npub use sonar_sim::executor;\npub use sonar_sim::funding;\npub use sonar_sim::idl_fetcher;\npub use sonar_sim::native_ids;\npub use sonar_sim::rpc_provider;\npub use sonar_sim::transaction;\npub use sonar_sim::types;\n```\n\n这样做的好处是 `handlers/`、`output/`、`parsers/` 中所有 `crate::core::xxx` 的引用无需修改。\n\n#### `src/utils/mod.rs`\n\n```rust\n// Before\npub(crate) mod config;\npub(crate) mod native_ids;\npub(crate) mod progress;\n\n// After（移除 native_ids）\npub(crate) mod config;\npub(crate) mod progress;\n```\n\n#### `src/utils/progress.rs` — 实现 ProgressReporter\n\n在现有 `Progress` 类型上添加 trait 实现：\n\n```rust\n// 在文件末尾添加\nimpl sonar_sim::progress::ProgressReporter for Progress {\n    fn set_message(\u0026self, msg: std::borrow::Cow\u003c'static, str\u003e) {\n        self.bar.set_message(msg);\n        self.bar.tick();\n    }\n\n    fn finish(\u0026self) {\n        self.bar.finish_and_clear();\n    }\n}\n```\n\n#### `src/handlers/simulate.rs` — 适配 Progress 类型\n\n```rust\n// Before\nlet account_loader = account_loader::AccountLoader::new(\n    rpc_url.clone(),\n    tx_cache_dir.clone(),\n    if offline { None } else { tx_cache_dir.clone() },\n    offline,\n    Some(progress.clone()),\n)?;\n\n// After\nuse std::sync::Arc;\nuse sonar_sim::progress::ProgressReporter;\n\nlet progress_arc: Arc\u003cdyn ProgressReporter\u003e = Arc::new(progress.clone());\nlet account_loader = account_loader::AccountLoader::new(\n    rpc_url.clone(),\n    tx_cache_dir.clone(),\n    if offline { None } else { tx_cache_dir.clone() },\n    offline,\n    Some(progress_arc.clone()),\n)?;\n```\n\nToken funding 调用也需适配：\n```rust\n// Before\nfunding::prepare_token_fundings(\u0026account_loader, \u0026mut resolved_accounts, \u0026token_funding_requests, Some(\u0026progress))?\n\n// After\nfunding::prepare_token_fundings(\u0026account_loader, \u0026mut resolved_accounts, \u0026token_funding_requests, Some(\u0026*progress_arc))?\n```\n\nIdlFetcher 构造方式变更：\n```rust\n// Before\nlet idl_fetcher = account_loader.idl_fetcher(Some(progress.clone()));\n\n// After\nlet idl_fetcher = IdlFetcher::with_provider(\n    account_loader.provider(),\n    Some(progress_arc.clone()),\n);\n```\n\n`fetch_transaction_from_rpc` 调用需移除 progress 参数：\n```rust\n// Before\ntransaction::parse_transaction_input(\u0026raw_input, \u0026rpc_url, Some(\u0026progress))?;\n\n// After\ntransaction::parse_transaction_input(\u0026raw_input, \u0026rpc_url)?;\n```\n\n同步修改 `parse_transaction_input` 的签名（在 sonar-sim 中已去掉 progress 参数）。\n\n#### `src/handlers/mod.rs` — 适配 Progress\n\n```rust\n// Before\npub(crate) fn auto_fetch_missing_idls(\n    idl_fetcher: \u0026idl_fetcher::IdlFetcher,\n    parser_registry: \u0026ParserRegistry,\n    program_ids: \u0026[Pubkey],\n    resolved_accounts: \u0026account_loader::ResolvedAccounts,\n    progress: Option\u003c\u0026Progress\u003e,\n) -\u003e Result\u003cusize\u003e {\n\n// After\npub(crate) fn auto_fetch_missing_idls(\n    idl_fetcher: \u0026idl_fetcher::IdlFetcher,\n    parser_registry: \u0026ParserRegistry,\n    program_ids: \u0026[Pubkey],\n    resolved_accounts: \u0026account_loader::ResolvedAccounts,\n    progress: Option\u003c\u0026dyn sonar_sim::progress::ProgressReporter\u003e,\n) -\u003e Result\u003cusize\u003e {\n```\n\n## 5. 依赖分割总览\n\n### sonar-sim 依赖\n\n| 类别 | 依赖 |\n|------|------|\n| 核心 | `litesvm`, `bincode` |\n| Solana SDK | `solana-account`, `solana-clock`, `solana-hash`, `solana-pubkey`, `solana-transaction`, `solana-message`, `solana-client`, `solana-commitment-config`, `solana-signature`, `solana-sdk-ids`, `solana-sysvar-id`, `solana-loader-v3-interface`, `solana-address-lookup-table-interface`, `solana-slot-hashes`, `solana-rent`, `solana-system-interface`, `solana-transaction-status-client-types`, `solana-rpc-client-types` |\n| SPL Token | `spl-token`, `spl-token-2022`, `spl-pod` |\n| 序列化 | `serde`, `serde_json`, `base64`, `bs58` |\n| 工具 | `anyhow`, `log`, `sha2`, `flate2`, `hex` |\n| 仅测试 | `solana-keypair`, `solana-signer` |\n\n### sonar CLI 保留依赖\n\n| 类别 | 依赖 |\n|------|------|\n| CLI | `clap`, `clap_complete` |\n| 日志 | `env_logger` |\n| UI | `colored`, `indicatif`, `terminal_size`, `unicode-width` |\n| 配置 | `toml`, `chrono` |\n| 解析 | `spl-token-metadata-interface`, `spl-token-group-interface`, `num-bigint` |\n| 核心引用 | `sonar-sim` |\n| 共用 | `anyhow`, `log`, `serde`, `serde_json`, `base64`, `bs58`, `bincode`, `hex`, `solana-account`, `solana-pubkey`, `solana-transaction`, `solana-message`, `solana-sdk-ids`, `solana-hash`, `solana-signature`, `solana-client`, `spl-token`, `spl-token-2022` |\n\n**注意**：某些 Solana 依赖同时被 `sonar-sim` 和 `sonar` CLI 使用（如 `solana-account`、`solana-pubkey`），因为 `output/`、`parsers/` 直接使用这些类型。版本需保持一致。\n\n## 6. 迁移步骤（执行顺序）\n\n### Phase 1: 创建 workspace 和空 crate\n\n1. 在根 `Cargo.toml` 中添加 `[workspace]` section\n2. 创建 `crates/sonar-sim/` 目录\n3. 创建 `crates/sonar-sim/Cargo.toml`\n4. 创建 `crates/sonar-sim/src/lib.rs`（空模块声明）\n5. 创建 `crates/sonar-sim/src/progress.rs`（ProgressReporter trait）\n6. 验证：`cargo build` 通过（sonar-sim 为空库）\n\n### Phase 2: 逐模块迁移（由简到难）\n\n按依赖顺序迁移，每迁移一个模块后运行 `cargo check` 确认编译通过：\n\n1. `types.rs`（无依赖，最简单）\n2. `native_ids.rs`（无内部依赖）\n3. `account_file.rs`（无内部依赖）\n4. `progress.rs`（已在 Phase 1 创建）\n5. `rpc_provider.rs`（无内部依赖）\n6. `balance_changes.rs`（无内部依赖）\n7. `transaction.rs`（依赖 progress → 移除 progress 参数）\n8. `cache.rs`（依赖 transaction）\n9. `idl_fetcher.rs`（依赖 rpc_provider, progress）\n10. `account_loader.rs`（依赖 rpc_provider, transaction, types, account_file, native_ids, progress）\n11. `funding/`（依赖 account_loader, types, progress）\n12. `executor.rs`（依赖 account_loader, funding, types, native_ids）\n\n### Phase 3: 更新 sonar CLI\n\n1. 将 `src/core/mod.rs` 替换为 re-export 层\n2. 删除 `src/core/` 下除 `mod.rs` 外的所有文件和 `funding/` 目录\n3. 删除 `src/utils/native_ids.rs`，更新 `src/utils/mod.rs`\n4. 在 `src/utils/progress.rs` 中添加 `ProgressReporter` impl\n5. 更新 `src/handlers/simulate.rs` 中的 Progress 用法\n6. 更新 `src/handlers/mod.rs` 中的 Progress 用法\n7. 更新根 `Cargo.toml` 依赖（添加 `sonar-sim`，移除已迁移的依赖）\n\n### Phase 4: 验证\n\n1. `cargo build` — workspace 两个 crate 均编译通过\n2. `cargo test` — 所有测试通过\n3. `cargo test -p sonar-sim` — library 测试独立运行\n4. `cargo clippy --workspace` — 无 warning\n5. 手动冒烟测试：`cargo run -- simulate \u003cTX\u003e` 功能正常\n\n## 7. 风险与注意事项\n\n| 风险 | 缓解措施 |\n|------|----------|\n| Solana crate 版本不一致导致类型不兼容 | workspace 统一管理版本，根 `Cargo.toml` 中使用 `[workspace.dependencies]` |\n| `litesvm` 类型在 crate 边界传递 | `TransactionMetadata` 在 `SimulationResult` 中被公开，确保 `litesvm` 版本一致 |\n| 测试中的 `FakeAccountProvider` 无法在 sonar 侧使用 | 将其从 `#[cfg(test)]` 提升为 `pu